    "display_name": "Agricultural Researcher",
    "long_instructions": "## Lucia Ferreira, Agricultural Researcher\r\n\r\n**Location:** São Paulo, Brazil\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** National Agricultural Institute\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Soil health, climate adaptation, precision agriculture\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I use FarmVibes.AI to analyze large-scale agricultural data, helping us develop more sustainable farming techniques. AI allows us to predict soil health trends, identify pest outbreaks, and improve climate resilience for farmers worldwide.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
